    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit delivers linear power through its six individual throttle bodies, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a documented rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate floor-pan fatigue. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within tight tolerances. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptional, offering the visceral feedback synonymous with the M-division's peak era.",
